description: Get your sweet-tooth fix with this easy tiramisu recipe. Using mud cake, coffee and cream, this decadent recipe is the perfect dessert hack.
name: Caramelised white choc tiramisu Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 600 g Woolworths caramelised white chocolate mud cake

recipeInstructions.text: Drizzle cake with coffee. Top with cream and spread to cover. Dust with cocoa and sprinkle with grated chocolate. Serve.
